&lt;Parlux Fragrances Inc> said itcompleted the offering of 420,000 unis at 10 dlrs each throughunderwriters R.C. Stamm and Co and Rosenkrantz Lyon and RossInc.    Each unit consists of two shares of common stock and oneredeemable warrant, which entitles the holder to buy anadditional common share for six dlrs between Feb 26, 1988 andFeb 26, 1992.    The company creates and markets fragrances and beautyproducts, including the "Anne Klein" line, through departmentand specialty stores. Reuter&#3;